th It)\n\n- **LinkedIn Sales Navigator:** $99/mo (if B2B)\n- **Hunter.io:** $49/mo (find email addresses)\n- **ConvertKit:** $29/mo (email marketing)\n- **Carrd Pro:** $19/year (custom domains)\n- **Calendly Pro:** $12/mo (multiple event types)\n\n### Communities\n\n- **Indie Hackers:** Free (indiehackers.com)\n- **r/SaaS:** Free (Reddit)\n- **r/entrepreneur:** Free (Reddit)\n- **Twitter #buildinpublic:** Free\n- **Product Hunt:** Free (producthunt.com)\n\n---\n\n## Mindset Shifts\n\n### From "Selling" to "Helping"\n\n**Old Mindset:** "I need to convince them to buy"\n\n**New Mindset:** "I need to understand if I can help them"\n\n**Result:** Lower pressure, better conversations, higher close rates\n\n---\n\n### From "Perfect Product" to "Progress"\n\n**Old Mindset:** "I can't sell until [feature] is done"\n\n**New Mindset:** "I'll sell the outcome and figure out the how"\n\n**Result:** Get customers faster, validate before over-building\n\n---\n\n### From "Rejection" to "Learning"\n\n**Old Mindset:** "They said no, I failed"\n\n**New Mindset:** "They said no, what can I learn?"\n\n**Result:** Every no gets you closer to yes, less emotional burnout\n\n---\n\n### From "One Big Win" to "Small Wins Daily"\n\n**Old Mindset:** "I need one customer to change everything"\n\n**New Mindset:** "I need 10 small activities every day"\n\n**Result:** Consistent progress, less anxiety, inevitable success\n\n---\n\n## Quick Reference\n\n### The 5-Customer Formula\n\n```\nCustomer #1: Warm network (friends, family, colleagues)\nCustomer #2: Cold outreach (targeted, personalized)\nCustomer #3: Content marketing (helpful, valuable)\nCustomer #4: Partnerships (win-win collaborations)\nCustomer #5: Paid ads (only after validation)\n```\n\n### Daily Non-Negotiables\n\n```\n☐ 5 warm outreaches\n☐ 10 cold outreaches\n☐ 5 community interactions\n☐ 1 piece of content\n☐ 10 follow-ups\n```\n\n### Weekly Goals\n\n```\n☐ 50+ total outreaches\n☐ 10+ responses\n☐ 5+ calls booked\n☐ 1-2 customers 